  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Each time a creature touches or deals damage as the result of a melee attack to you, it takes 2d6 Acid damage. <br />Additionally, any weapon used to strike you suffers a permanent and cumulative −1 penalty to damage rolls. <br />The weapon is destroyed if the penalty ever reaches −5. <br />Casting Mending would remove all penalty stacks.</p>",
